    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Political Approval\"\nsubtitle: \"Gallup per-administration averages, 1999 to present\"\n---\n\n\n\nGallup's *job approval* question is the longest continuous polling series of\nits kind. The numbers below are **term-average approval ratings** — not\nsnapshot polls. They tell you what percentage of Americans, on average\nacross each president's entire term, answered \"approve\" when asked whether\nthey approved of the job the president was doing.\n\n::: {.callout-note appearance=\"simple\"}\nGallup approval is not available from a free API; the values in\n`gallup_approval.csv` are **hand-curated** from Gallup's published summaries\nand updated on demand, not daily. The *economic-sentiment* portion of this\nsite refreshes daily from FRED; this section does not.\n:::\n\n## Per-administration average {#avg}\n\nHorizontal reference line: the average of completed admins' averages\n(47.1%).\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"echarts4r html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-3d52bc671b0fd1ec9385\" style=\"width:100%;height:500px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-3d52bc671b0fd1ec9385\">{\"x\":{\"theme\":\"custom\",\"tl\":false,\"draw\":true,\"renderer\":\"canvas\",\"events\":[],\"buttons\":[],\"opts\":{\"yAxis\":[{\"show\":true,\"name\":\"%\",\"axisLabel\":{\"formatter\":\"{value}%\"},\"min\":30,\"max\":70}],\"xAxis\":[{\"data\":[\"Clinton\",\"Bush (43)\",\"Obama\",\"Trump I\",\"Biden\"],\"type\":\"category\",\"boundaryGap\":true}],\"legend\":{\"data\":[\"Gallup approval avg (%)\"]},\"series\":[{\"data\":[{\"value\":[\"Clinton\",\"55.1\"]},{\"value\":[\"Bush (43)\",\"49.4\"]},{\"value\":[\"Obama\",\"47.9\"]},{\"value\":[\"Trump I\",\"41.0\"]},{\"value\":[\"Biden\",\"42.2\"]}],\"name\":\"Gallup approval avg (%)\",\"type\":\"bar\",\"yAxisIndex\":0,\"xAxisIndex\":0,\"coordinateSystem\":\"cartesian2d\",\"itemStyle\":{\"color\":\"function(p){ var c=[\\\"#2a6f97\\\",\\\"#bc4749\\\",\\\"#2a6f97\\\",\\\"#bc4749\\\",\\\"#2a6f97\\\",\\\"#bc4749\\\"]; return c[p.dataIndex]; }\"},\"markLine\":{\"lineStyle\":{\"type\":\"dashed\",\"color\":\"#6c757d\"},\"label\":{\"formatter\":\"Baseline (47.1%)\",\"position\":\"end\"},\"data\":[{\"yAxis\":47.1}]}}],\"tooltip\":{\"trigger\":\"axis\",\"valueFormatter\":\"function(v){ return typeof v==='number' ? v.toFixed(1)+'%' : v; }\"},\"title\":[{\"left\":\"center\",\"text\":\"Gallup approval: term average per administration\"}]},\"dispose\":true,\"theme2\":true,\"customTheme\":\"{\\n  \\\"color\\\": [\\\"#2a6f97\\\",\\\"#e07a5f\\\",\\\"#bc4749\\\",\\\"#6a4c93\\\",\\\"#2f9e44\\\",\\\"#f2c14e\\\",\\\"#1d3557\\\",\\\"#6c757d\\\"],\\n  \\\"backgroundColor\\\": \\\"transparent\\\",\\n  \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"fontFamily\\\": \\\"system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif\\\" },\\n  \\\"title\\\": { \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"fontWeight\\\": \\\"600\\\" } },\\n  \\\"legend\\\": { \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#495057\\\" } },\\n  \\\"grid\\\": { \\\"containLabel\\\": true, \\\"left\\\": 48, \\\"right\\\": 24, \\\"top\\\": 56, \\\"bottom\\\": 40 },\\n  \\\"xAxis\\\": { \\\"axisLine\\\": { \\\"lineStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#adb5bd\\\" } } },\\n  \\\"yAxis\\\": { \\\"splitLine\\\": { \\\"lineStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#e9ecef\\\" } } }\\n}\",\"theme_name\":\"econ\"},\"evals\":[\"opts.series.0.itemStyle.color\",\"opts.tooltip.valueFormatter\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Range: min to max during each term {#range}\n\nPresidents often peak early (honeymoon) or after major rallying events (9/11),\nand decline late. The bars below show the full min–max range each president\ntraversed, with a dot marking their term-average.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-f97070f36f2b51d028b9\" style=\"width:100%;height:325px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-f97070f36f2b51d028b9\">{\"x\":{\"visdat\":{\"17c225d920121\":[\"function () \",\"plotlyVisDat\"]},\"cur_data\":\"17c225d920121\",\"attrs\":{\"17c225d920121\":{\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"x\":{},\"y\":{},\"base\":{},\"type\":\"bar\",\"name\":\"Min – Max range\",\"marker\":{\"color\":{},\"line\":{\"color\":{},\"width\":1}},\"width\":0.40000000000000002,\"hovertemplate\":\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"customdata\":{},\"inherit\":true},\"17c225d920121.1\":{\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"x\":{},\"y\":{},\"type\":\"scatter\",\"mode\":\"markers\",\"name\":\"Term average\",\"marker\":{\"symbol\":\"diamond\",\"size\":11,\"color\":\"#1d3557\"},\"hovertemplate\":\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"inherit\":true},\"17c225d920121.2\":{\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"x\":{},\"y\":{},\"type\":\"scatter\",\"mode\":\"markers\",\"name\":\"Exit approval\",\"marker\":{\"symbol\":\"circle\",\"size\":11,\"color\":\"#bc4749\"},\"hovertemplate\":\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"inherit\":true}},\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"b\":50,\"l\":50,\"t\":30,\"r\":30},\"xaxis\":{\"domain\":[0,1],\"automargin\":true,\"title\":\"\",\"type\":\"category\",\"categoryorder\":\"array\",\"categoryarray\":[\"Biden\",\"Bush (43)\",\"Clinton\",\"Obama\",\"Trump I\"]},\"yaxis\":{\"domain\":[0,1],\"automargin\":true,\"title\":\"Approval (%)\",\"range\":[20,95]},\"legend\":{\"orientation\":\"h\",\"y\":1.1000000000000001,\"x\":0.5,\"xanchor\":\"center\"},\"barmode\":\"overlay\",\"hovermode\":\"closest\",\"showlegend\":true},\"source\":\"A\",\"config\":{\"modeBarButtonsToAdd\":[\"hoverclosest\",\"hovercompare\"],\"showSendToCloud\":false,\"displayModeBar\":false},\"data\":[{\"x\":[\"Clinton\",\"Bush (43)\",\"Obama\",\"Trump I\",\"Biden\"],\"y\":[36,65,27,15,20],\"base\":[37,25,40,34,37],\"type\":\"bar\",\"name\":\"Min – Max range\",\"marker\":{\"color\":[\"#2a6f9766\",\"#bc474966\",\"#2a6f9766\",\"#bc474966\",\"#2a6f9766\"],\"line\":{\"color\":[\"#2a6f97\",\"#bc4749\",\"#2a6f97\",\"#bc4749\",\"#2a6f97\"],\"width\":1}},\"width\":[0.40000000000000002,0.40000000000000002,0.40000000000000002,0.40000000000000002,0.40000000000000002],\"hovertemplate\":[\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Min: %{base:.0f}%<br>Max: %{customdata:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\"],\"customdata\":[73,90,67,49,57],\"error_y\":{\"color\":\"rgba(31,119,180,1)\"},\"error_x\":{\"color\":\"rgba(31,119,180,1)\"},\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"frame\":null},{\"x\":[\"Clinton\",\"Bush (43)\",\"Obama\",\"Trump I\",\"Biden\"],\"y\":[55.100000000000001,49.399999999999999,47.899999999999999,41,42.200000000000003],\"type\":\"scatter\",\"mode\":\"markers\",\"name\":\"Term average\",\"marker\":{\"color\":\"#1d3557\",\"symbol\":\"diamond\",\"size\":11,\"line\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,127,14,1)\"}},\"hovertemplate\":[\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Avg: %{y:.1f}%<extra><\\/extra>\"],\"error_y\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,127,14,1)\"},\"error_x\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,127,14,1)\"},\"line\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,127,14,1)\"},\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"frame\":null},{\"x\":[\"Clinton\",\"Bush (43)\",\"Obama\",\"Trump I\",\"Biden\"],\"y\":[66,34,59,34,38],\"type\":\"scatter\",\"mode\":\"markers\",\"name\":\"Exit approval\",\"marker\":{\"color\":\"#bc4749\",\"symbol\":\"circle\",\"size\":11,\"line\":{\"color\":\"rgba(44,160,44,1)\"}},\"hovertemplate\":[\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\",\"%{x}<br>Exit: %{y:.0f}%<extra><\\/extra>\"],\"error_y\":{\"color\":\"rgba(44,160,44,1)\"},\"error_x\":{\"color\":\"rgba(44,160,44,1)\"},\"line\":{\"color\":\"rgba(44,160,44,1)\"},\"xaxis\":\"x\",\"yaxis\":\"y\",\"frame\":null}],\"highlight\":{\"on\":\"plotly_click\",\"persistent\":false,\"dynamic\":false,\"selectize\":false,\"opacityDim\":0.20000000000000001,\"selected\":{\"opacity\":1},\"debounce\":0},\"shinyEvents\":[\"plotly_hover\",\"plotly_click\",\"plotly_selected\",\"plotly_relayout\",\"plotly_brushed\",\"plotly_brushing\",\"plotly_clickannotation\",\"plotly_doubleclick\",\"plotly_deselect\",\"plotly_afterplot\",\"plotly_sunburstclick\"],\"base_url\":\"https://plot.ly\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Detailed Gallup table {#table}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"reactable html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-e15178be36da39a053dc\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-e15178be36da39a053dc\">{\"x\":{\"tag\":{\"name\":\"Reactable\",\"attribs\":{\"data\":{\"president\":[\"Bill Clinton\",\"George W. Bush\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Joe Biden\",\"Donald Trump (2nd term) *\"],\"party\":[\"Democratic\",\"Republican\",\"Democratic\",\"Republican\",\"Democratic\",\"Republican\"],\"avg_approval\":[55.1,49.4,47.9,41,42.2,\"NA\"],\"min_approval\":[37,25,40,34,37,\"NA\"],\"max_approval\":[73,90,67,49,57,\"NA\"],\"last_approval\":[66,34,59,34,38,\"NA\"],\"notes\":[\"8-year term avg; 66% exit approval, highest modern exit.\",\"Max 90% post-9/11; collapsed to 25% by end of term.\",\"Max 67% early in term; exit approval 59%.\",\"Never reached 50% — first president in Gallup polling history with that record.\",\"Max 57% early; fell to high-30s after Afghanistan withdrawal and inflation peak.\",\"Ongoing — updated on demand.\"]},\"columns\":[{\"id\":\"president\",\"name\":\"President\",\"type\":\"character\",\"minWidth\":180},{\"id\":\"party\",\"name\":\"Party\",\"type\":\"character\",\"cell\":[{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#bc4749\"}},\"children\":[\"REPUBLICAN\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#bc4749\"}},\"children\":[\"REPUBLICAN\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.72rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#bc4749\"}},\"children\":[\"REPUBLICAN\"]}],\"html\":true,\"minWidth\":110},{\"id\":\"avg_approval\",\"name\":\"Avg (%)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"suffix\":\"%\",\"digits\":1},\"aggregated\":{\"suffix\":\"%\",\"digits\":1}},\"style\":{\"fontWeight\":600}},{\"id\":\"min_approval\",\"name\":\"Min (%)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"},\"aggregated\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"}}},{\"id\":\"max_approval\",\"name\":\"Max (%)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"},\"aggregated\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"}}},{\"id\":\"last_approval\",\"name\":\"Exit (%)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"},\"aggregated\":{\"suffix\":\"%\"}}},{\"id\":\"notes\",\"name\":\"Notes\",\"type\":\"character\",\"minWidth\":320}],\"highlight\":true,\"striped\":true,\"compact\":true,\"theme\":{\"borderColor\":\"#dee2e6\"},\"dataKey\":\"20c5700de9367e83109e3513db6a0429\"},\"children\":[]},\"class\":\"reactR_markup\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Sources\n\n- **Gallup News:** *Presidential Job Approval Center.*\n  <https://news.gallup.com/interactives/185273/presidential-job-approval-center.aspx>\n- **The American Presidency Project (UCSB):** *Presidential Job Approval Tables.*\n  <https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/statistics/data/presidential-job-approval>\n\nAggregate averages are facts in the *Feist v. Rural* sense (not copyrightable),\nbut survey methodology and phrasing vary across polling firms. These figures\nuse Gallup's consistent methodology throughout.\n",
